                  Guillermo Suarez{-}Tangil and
                  Dave Levin and
                  Cristel Pelsser},
	title = {Poster: Building Comprehensive Telecommunications Datasets During
                  a Major Climatic Event},
	booktitle = {Proceedings of the 2024 {ACM} on Internet Measurement Conference,
                  {IMC} 2024, Madrid, Spain, November 4-6, 2024},
	pages = {781--782},
	publisher = {{ACM}},
